es="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>黑手党戏剧<i>《中音骑士》</i>在星期五（3月21日）上电影院，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-de-niro">罗伯特·德·尼罗（Robert de Niro）</a>是否扮演两个主角？请继续阅读所有信息。</p><p>这部电影是由尼古拉斯·皮尔吉（Nicholas Pileggi）撰写的，他还为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/martin-scorsese">马丁·斯科塞斯（Martin Scorsese）</a>的《好人》（ <i>Goodfellas）</i>共同撰写了剧本，这是他自己的书<i>《怀塞吉（Wiseguy）</i>的改编》，由巴里·莱文森（Barry Levinson）执导，巴里·列文森（Barry Levinson）以<i>卧铺</i>，<i>雨人和</i><i>好早晨</i>而闻名。</p><p>这部电影描绘了两个现实生活中的高级黑手党老板Vito Genovese和Frank Costello之间的权力斗争。当维托对弗兰克（Frank）命令打击弗兰克（Frank）时，他们的竞争爆发了冲突，后者在计划退休时努力保护他的家人。</p><p>在这里查看电影的预告片： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="中音骑士|官方拖车" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1aayuOp0AnE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> In real-life, Genovese was a close associate of Lucky Luciano, a major force in US organised crime, in the &#39;40s and &#39;50s, before becoming head of his own crime family.对Costello的尝试发生在1957年，Genovese随后召集了黑手党峰会以巩固他的权力。 However, his reign was cut short two years later when he was convicted on narcotics conspiracy charges and sentenced to 15 years in prison.</p><h2> Is Robert De Niro playing both characters in <i>The Alto Knights</i> ?</h2><p> Yes, De Niro does in fact play both key roles in <i>The Alto Knights</i> . As seen in the trailer above, the acting legend is made up and dressed differently to differentiate the two characters.</p><p> It is not the first time De Niro has portrayed roles with connections to organised crime. One of his breakthrough roles came in Francis Ford Coppola&#39;s <i>The Godfather Part II</i> (1974), where he played the young Vito Corleone in New York in the early 20th century.</p><p> He also played seasoned gangster Jimmy Conway in <i>Goodfellas</i> (1990) and casino operator Sam &#39;Ace&#39; Rothstein in <i>Casino</i> (1995), two films co-written by Nicholas Pileggi, as is <i>The Alto Knights</i> .</p><p> More recently, he played Frank Sheeran, a mob hitman and union official with crime family ties in Martin Scorsese&#39;s <i>The Irishman</i> in 2019.</p><p> <em>The Alto Knights</em> is in cinemas around the world now.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/is-robert-de-niro-playing-both-characters-in-the-alto-knights-3847796">Is Robert De Niro playing both characters in &#39;The Alto Knights&#39;?</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
